<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmanu mahāmaṁḍalēśvara 
<lb n="2"/>rudradēvamahārājulu prithivirājya 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mu sēyaṁgānu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti samasta bhu 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vana jana vikhyāta paṁcaśata vīraśā 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>sana śabdānēka guṇaguṇālaṁkrita sa 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>tya śauca cāru caritra nayava<unclear>pu</unclear>lla 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>gyāya vīrabalaṁ jyōtsava dharmma pra 
<lb n="8" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ti pālitulaina śrīmatu yi 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>jeyanānādēsinipa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> nā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/>munugāvisi dīni meṭamaṭastala 
<lb n="11" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> siperumāṁḍi seṭṭini me 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>vini tammulaina rudradēvarājula 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>rāyurārōgyavīriyyābhivriddhigā 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ga <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> śarra śrīmanumahādēva 
<lb n="15"/>cennakēśavadēvarakunu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī 
<lb n="16"/><unclear>śaka</unclear>varuṣaṁbulu 11<unclear>9</unclear>0 Agunēṁṭi 
<lb n="17"/><unclear>vibha</unclear>va saṁvatsara kārtti<unclear>ka</unclear> ba 15 ma sūyya 
<lb n="18" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> na yi dēvaraku dīpānaku suṁka 
<lb n="19"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> pōtulu 10 dīnina dapina<unclear>vāru</unclear> 
<lb n="20"/>śrī vaikuṁṭhāna dēvakanyalu 
<lb n="21"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> luḍaṁgānuṁḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> dīninaḍa <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="22"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ka vighnamusēsinavāru śrī 
<lb n="23"/>vāraṇāsi kaṟuta braṁhmāna 
<lb n="24"/>gōvulavadhiṁcena dōṣāna 
<lb n="25"/><unclear>bō</unclear>vuvāru 
